          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "In the evening a British family arrive. They have a small, white and fluffy dog named Marley. Marley meets the three village dogs and is immediately in love. Well call it love or hormones as one of the three dogs is on heat. There’s some humping and suddenly the torches are out and British voices call for their dog. “Marley is off shagging the locals” the daughter remarks. ",
            "link": null
